graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>v1.21.0-18]

    %% External Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 18.0.0+]
    Dashboard -->|framework| React[React 18.2.0]
    Dashboard -->|UI library| PatternFly[PatternFly 5.3.x]
    Dashboard -->|backend| Fastify[Fastify 4.16.0]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient[Kubernetes Client 0.12.2]
    Dashboard -->|auth gateway| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>openshift4/ose-oauth-proxy]

    %% Core Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    Dashboard -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Dashboard -->|metrics queries| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTP]
    Dashboard -->|image inspection| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Internal ODH Component Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|monitors CRs| ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster/DSCInit]
    Dashboard -->|CRUD notebooks| KubeflowNotebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRs]
    Dashboard -->|reads templates| KServe[KServe<br/>ServingRuntime CRs]
    Dashboard -->|manages instances| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CRs]
    Dashboard -->|creates builds| OpenShiftBuild[OpenShift Build Service<br/>BuildConfigs]

    %% Integration Points
    ODHConsole[ODH Console Links] -.->|links to| Dashboard
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|UI integration| Dashboard

    %% External Services
    Dashboard -->|storage access| S3[S3 Storage<br/>optional]

